<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>pa viṇ poruñ
<lb n="2" break="no"/>cikaramātira veṇ
<lb n="3" break="no"/>koṭṭeṇ peru
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṅkaḷiṟu vicai maka
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ḷoṭu voṉpatu 
<lb n="6"/>kaṇṭattuyar pula
<lb n="7"/>ventaraṉpuṭaṉ
<lb n="8"/>vaṇaṅkiyarun tiṉa
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ṟkāṭṭiyaṇi taṭamu
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ṭimelaṭi malar cūṭi
<lb n="11"/>maṇimuṭi cūṭi vaḷaṅ
<lb n="12" break="no"/>keḻu kavari cēra ce
<lb n="13" break="no"/>mpiyar tiraṇṭaruka
<lb n="14" break="no"/>caippa viraciṅkāta
<lb n="15" break="no"/>ṉa peru nāppaṭa kaṭa
</p>

<p>Next face.</p>

<p>
<lb n="16" break="no"/>vuḷ miṉ<unclear>ṉa</unclear> kaṟput ti
<lb n="17" break="no"/>kaḻvuṭaṉ muṭicūṭiyu
<lb n="18" break="no"/>lakam poṟṟac ceru
<lb n="19"/>malitāṉaip pārpu
<lb n="20" break="no"/>ra ventarāṭakat
<lb n="21"/>toḷumākamum piri
<lb n="22" break="no"/>yāvoṭari neṭuṅ
<lb n="23" break="no"/>kaṇoṇṭoṭi ma
<lb n="24" break="no"/>kaḷir tilata nutal
<lb n="25"/>meṟ cevaṭivaikku
<lb n="26" break="no"/>mulaka muḻutuṭaiyā
</p>

<p>Next face.</p>

<p>
<lb n="27" break="no"/>roṭum viṟṟirunta
<lb n="28" break="no"/>ruḷiya māmati matikku
<lb n="29" break="no"/>lam viḷakkiya kō
<lb n="30" break="no"/>mutaṟ koccaṭai
<lb n="31" break="no"/>yava<hi rend="grantha">rmma</hi>(ma)rāṉa <hi rend="grantha">tri</hi>
<lb n="32" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">bhu</hi>vaṉac cakkaravat 
<lb n="33" break="no"/>tikaḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>kula<hi rend="grantha">śekha</hi>
<lb n="34" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">rade</hi>vaṟ(r)kku yāṇṭu
<lb n="35"/>2raṇṭāvatu nāḷ
<lb n="36"/>muppattaiñciṉāl
<lb n="37"/>maturotaya vaḷa
<lb n="38" break="no"/>nāṭṭu māṭakkuḷak
<lb n="39" break="no"/>kiḻmaturaik ko
<lb n="40" break="no"/>yiṟ paḷḷiyaṟaikka
</p>

